(1, 'Mengatasi Kecanduan Alkohol', 'Di sejumlah budaya tertentu alkohol menjadi minuman favorit. Banyak orang menghubungkan alkohol dengan kesenangan.', 'images/31cba38836c4b7bd71d897bbb9a5412e.png', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 16.7999pt; text-indent: -13.2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -13.2pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%;">Di sejumlah budaya tertentu alkohol menjadi minuman favorit. Banyak orang menghubungkan alkohol dengan kesenangan, relasi sosial, dan perayaan. Kita juga dapat menggunakan alkohol untuk membuat kita merasa lebih baik pada saat kita merasa tertekan atau tidak bahagia, atau untuk meningkatkan rasa percaya diri.</span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\n110%;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; </span><span lang="id" style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Sebagai mahasiswa Anda dalam kondisi yang rentan. Jika anda berada jauh dari keluarga maupun rumah dan ada di dalam lingkungan baru, ada banyak pengalaman baru untuk dipelajari, namun banyak juga hal yang berpotensi untuk menimbulkan stres.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%;">Anda mungkin merasa tidak yakin dengan kemampuan akademis Anda. Anda mungkin harus mengelola hidup Anda dalam cara yang belum pernah Anda lakukan sebelumnya. Menyeimbangkan kehidupan kuliah/bekerja dengan relasi sosial bisa jadi menjadi sesuatu yang sulit untuk dilakukan. Anda mungkin khawatir tentang masalah keuangan, atau</span><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%;">relasi, atau daya tarik fisik.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><img class="img-responsive" src="../images/d1c88f8d57afab699f8e16e53ee09d1a9.png" data-filename="Capture.PNG" style="width: 25%; float: right;"><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 110%;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Batas yang dianggap aman untuk konsumsi alkohol adalah sebanyak 2-3 unit per hari untuk perempuan dan sebanyak 3-4 unit untuk pria (sampai dengan 2 liter per hari). Konsumsi alkohol yang melebihi takaran tersebut secara terus menerus akan meningkatkan resiko ancaman terhadap kesehatan Anda. Setelah Anda mabuk, Anda sebaiknya menghindari konsumsi alkohol selama paling sedikitnya 48 jam untuk memberikan waktu bagi tubuh memulihkan kerusakan pada hati.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">Bila Anda mengenali adanya satu atau dua gejala berikut ini, berarti sudah waktunya bagi Anda untuk melakukan sesuatu:</span><br></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 16.7999pt; text-indent: -14.4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span style="width:9.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Kebiasaan minum Anda seringkali tidak dapat Anda kendalikan dan semakin menjadi-jadi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 16.7999pt; text-indent: -14.4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span style="width:9.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Anda secara teratur mengkonsumsi alkohol melebih batas aman yang dianjurkan.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 16.7999pt; text-indent: -14.4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Anda mungkin mengkonsumsi alkohol lebih banyak untuk mendapatkan efek yang sama seperti sebelumnya, atau minum di pagi hari, atau minum sendiri.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:-13.2pt;\nmargin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:\n50%;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.2pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Dalam hal studi, Anda mungkin mengalami kesulitan dalam berkonsentrasi, suasana hati yang berubah-ubah dan didera perasaan bersalah.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:-13.2pt;\nmargin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:\n50%;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.2pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Relasi dengan orang lain menurun atau berkurang, dan penampilan dan gaya hidup Anda dipengaruhi oleh kebutuhan untuk mengkonsumi alkohol.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:-13.2pt;\nmargin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:\n50%;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.2pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Ketika Anda mencoba berhenti minum alkohol, Anda menyadari secara fisik Anda berkeringat, tremor (</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">gerakan pada anggota</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">/</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">bagian tubuh yang tidak terkontrol</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">/</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">di luar kemauan</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">)</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">, dan gelisah.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:-13.2pt;\nmargin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:\n50%;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.2pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">· </span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Sebagian besar peminum&nbsp; dapat berhenti tanpa harus menjadi kecanduan, namun hal ini sangat jarang terjadi pada mahasiswa.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"> </span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:\n-14.4pt;margin-bottom:0pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;\nmso-level-size:10.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:14.4pt"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Perilaku minum Anda sebagai mahasiswa tergantung pada konteks dan lingkungan di mana Anda berada.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">Alkohol dengan mudah diasosiasikan dengan sejumlah permasalahan dan transisi yang sedang Anda hadapi sebagai mahasiswa. Kemampuan alkohol untuk membuat Anda merasa santai, mengurangi tekanan dan hilang kesadaran, membuat alkohol digunakan untuk menghindari atau&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">menghadapi situasi sulit. Situasi sulit tersebut misalnya kehilangan, perpisahan, seks, hubungan, dan tanggung jawab. Minum di bar membuat Anda merasa santai dengan berada di dalam komunitas yang sama, namun kebiasaan ini membuat Anda sulit menjadi santai bila tidak melakukannya.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 16.7999pt; text-indent: -14.4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><img class="img-responsive" src="../images/9358487f23765ca7bd7806daee4ecc145.png" data-filename="Capture2.PNG" style="width: 50%;"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:16.7999pt;text-indent:\n-14.4pt;margin-bottom:0pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;\nmso-level-size:10.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:14.4pt"></p><div style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Berlin Sans FB"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"><br></span></font></div><span lang="en-US" style="line-height: 1.5;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-US" style="line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -14.4pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -14.4pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">Berikut ini beberapa ide yang dapat menolong Anda untuk menurunkan konsumsi alkohol Anda:</span></div></span>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 13.9355pt; text-indent: -13.9355pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Buatlah catatan harian mengenai kebiasaan minum Anda untuk memetakan pola penggunaan dan jumlah konsumsi alkohol Anda. Menurunkan kebiasaan minum dapat berhasil bila Anda menetapkan batas yang masuk akal untuk Anda tepati.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 13.9355pt; text-indent: -13.9355pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">· &nbsp;</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Identifkasi kesempatan, waktu, teman, ataupun suasana hati yang berpotensi membuat Anda rentan mengkonsumsi alkohol.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 13.9355pt; text-indent: -13.9355pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Daripada hanya berfokus pada menurunkan konsumsi alkohol, berpikirlah untuk meningkatkan aktivitas lain. Ada banyak kesempatan baru dan berbeda untuk Anda lakukan selama kuliah. Gunakanlah kesempatan tersebut, Anda mungkin dapat “menemukan” sisi kepribadian yang belum Anda ketahui sebelumnya.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 13.9355pt; text-indent: -13.9355pt;"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Orang lain dapat memberikan pengaruh yang kuat, karena itu gunakanlah hal ini untuk mendukung upaya Anda menurunkan konsumsi alkohol. Mungkin selama ini memang ada teman-teman yang memang peduli dan khawatir dengan kebiasaan minum Anda</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:13.9355pt;text-indent:\n-13.9355pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.9355pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Akan sangat menolong bila Anda menuliskan di sebuah kertas mengenai sisi pro dan kontranya mengkonsumsi alkohol; untuk melihat dengan seksama apakah Anda betul-betul memiliki tekad yang kuat untuk berhenti minum.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:13.9355pt;text-indent:\n-13.9355pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.9355pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Lebih baik meminum alkohol sebagai pendamping makanan, bukan sebagai pengganti makanan.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:13.9355pt;text-indent:\n-13.9355pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:13.9355pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:8.5pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Anda dapat mencoba menghadiri pertemuan kelompok khusus orang-orang yang ingin berhenti minum alkohol.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 13.9355pt; text-indent: -13.9355pt;"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="id" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-weight: bold;">Menolong Orang Lain</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB''; font-weight: bold;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Anda dapat merasa sangat tertekan bila orang yang Anda kasihi memiliki kebiasaan minum alkohol sampai pada taraf di mana kebiasaan tersebut menimbulkan masalah bagi dirinya maupun orang lain.&nbsp;</span></div><img class="img-responsive" src="../images/fe4517e604e61207f4b6f420f781ad7012.png" data-filename="Picture12.png" style="text-align: justify; width: 41.6609px; height: 70px; float: right;"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">Meskipun Anda dapat mendorong dan mendukung mereka untuk berubah, namun tetap mereka sendirilah yang pada akhirnya harus membuat keputusan (dan bersiap) untuk membuat perubahan.</span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;"><br></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 0pt;">Bila Anda peka dengan alkohol (misalnya karena mengalami masalah ini dalam keluarga Anda) ingatlah beberapa hal berikut ini yang mungkin dapat menolong Anda.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;"><br></span></div></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 12pt;">·</span><span style="width:1.75pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Berikan ruang untuk mereka (orang yang memiliki kebiasaan minum) membicarakan apa saja yang mengganggu/menjadi masalah untuk mereka.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 12pt;">·</span><span style="width:1.75pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Daripada melabel mereka, fokuskan pada dampak perilaku minum yang mereka lakukan pada orang lain dan diri mereka.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 12pt;">·</span><span style="width:1.75pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Perjelas perilaku apa yang tidak dapat Anda tolerir dan hindari adu argumentasi.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 12pt;">·</span><span style="width:1.75pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Jangan berbohong untuk mereka atau menutupi perilaku mereka</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 12pt;">·</span><span style="width:1.75pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">P</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">astikan bahwa Anda bukan satu-satunya orang yang menanggung beban untuk mendukung mereka, dan Anda perlu menyediakan waktu untuk diri Anda sendiri</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Sambil membaca leaflet ini, Anda mungkin mulai dapat mengenali aspek-aspek yang relevan dengan situasi yang Anda hadapi saat ini atau situasi yang Anda khawatirkan Anda berpotensi untuk terjerumus masuk ke dalamnya. Kadang-kadang membicarakan masalah Anda dengan orang lain dapat menolong Anda untuk menjernihkan pikiran, perasaan dan tindakan Anda. </span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:7.7538pt;text-indent:-7.7538pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;mso-level-number-format:\nbullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:12.0pt;mso-level-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-level-indent:7.7538pt"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">\n\n</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Ada beberapa sumber pertolongan yang dapat dipercaya : <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:11.0769pt;text-indent:\n-11.0769pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:11.0769pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:6.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Dosen/pembimbing</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-greek-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Calibri;mso-armenian-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Calibri;mso-arabic-font-family:Calibri;mso-currency-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-latinext-font-family:Calibri;language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:11.0769pt;text-indent:\n-11.0769pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:11.0769pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:6.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Dokter maupun perawat </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">di Poliklinik (mintalah pemeriksaan medis bila memang Anda merasa khawatir dengan kondisi tubuh Anda)</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-greek-font-family:Calibri;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Calibri;mso-hebrew-font-family:Calibri;mso-arabic-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-currency-font-family:Calibri;mso-latinext-font-family:Calibri;\nlanguage:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-left:11.0769pt;text-indent:\n-11.0769pt;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:11.0769pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span><span style="width:6.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:\nnone">PKBI Sahaja (Perkumpulan Keluarga Berencana Sahabat Remaja)</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-greek-font-family:Calibri;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Calibri;mso-hebrew-font-family:Calibri;mso-arabic-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-currency-font-family:Calibri;mso-latinext-font-family:Calibri;\nlanguage:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="id" style="font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-greek-font-family:Calibri;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Calibri;mso-armenian-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hebrew-font-family:Calibri;mso-arabic-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-currency-font-family:Calibri;mso-latinext-font-family:Calibri;language:\nid;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="id" style="font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;\nmso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none">Selain pihak-pihak yang sudah disebut di atas, tentu saja konselor di Pusat Pengembangan Pribadi bersedia menjadi teman cerita dan menolong Anda mencari solusi yang terbaik bagi Anda. Kami bersedia menolong untuk menyelesaikan masalah yang mendasari mengapa Anda minum alkohol secara berlebihan, tapi biasanya kami akan merujuk Anda ke tenaga profesional yang lebih kompeten bila Anda mengalami kecanduan ataupun membutuhkan pertolongan medis.</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none"> </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;\nmso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="id" style="font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;\nmso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;\nmso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none">Di Pusat Pengembangan Pribadi tersedia sejumlah </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none">leaflet</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-armenian-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;mso-ligatures:none"> dengan berbagai macam topik yang berguna untuk menolong Anda. Anda dapat memperolehnya di bagian resepsionis (Anda tidak harus menyebutkan informasi apa yang Anda perlukan ataupun bertemu dengan konselor terlebih dahulu).</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none"> </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-default-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;mso-latin-font-family:\n&quot;Berlin Sans FB&quot;;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-bidi-language:ar-SA;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family: ''Berlin Sans FB'';">Sumber : </span><a href="http://www.counselling.cam.ac.uk/selfhelp/leaflets/alcohol"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family: