bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Hal ini </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria; text-transform: uppercase;">terutama</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;"> bagi seseorang yang benar-benar belum mengetahui tentang bidang apa yang dapat ia kuasai dengan baik. Bakat dapat berupa apa saja, tidak hanya terbatas pada kemampuan-kemampuan kognitif.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-weight: bold;"><span dir="ltr"></span>2. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">Refleksi pada masa lalu<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Ingat-ingat tentang pencapaian apa saja yang pernah kamu dapatkan dan hal-hal apa yang paling kamu sukai dan kamu banggakan.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;tab-stops:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">3. Pikirkan kegiatan apa yang membuatmu senang<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Bakat bisa muncul dari kegiatan atau aktivitas sehari-hari yang sangat disukai sehingga seseorang akan senang ketika melakukannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">4. Evaluasi tentang apa yang kamu kuasai<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;tab-stops:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Hal ini berbeda dengan poin sebelumnya. Terkadang seseorang memiliki suatu kemampuan pada bidang tertentu, namun ia tidak terlalu tertarik untuk melakukannya sehingga lama-kelamaan bakat tersebut hilang. Oleh karena itu kedua poin ini (</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria; text-decoration: underline;">hal yang membuat senang dan hal yang dikuasai</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">) harus dipikirkan secara matang sebelum membuat kesimpulan tentang bakat yang dimiliki.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;tab-stops:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-35.446pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-weight: bold;"><span dir="ltr"></span>5. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">Bertanya<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Tanyakanlah pada orang-orang terdekatmu seperti keluarga atau sahabat tentang hal apa yang dapat kamu lakukan dengan baik. Siapa tahu orang lain telah melihat bakat dalam dirimu yang belum kamu sadari.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">6. Sisihkan waktu pribadi</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">Bersantailah dengan dirimu sendiri. Cobalah hal-hal baru yang belum pernah atau belum sempat kamu coba. Waktu yang berkualitas dengan diri sendiri sangat membantu dalam </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria; font-style: italic;">self-discovery </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">sehingga dapat membuka potensi-potensi yang masih tersembunyi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Dotum;mso-ascii-font-family:\nDotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:Dotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nDotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:Dotum;mso-hangul-font-family:\nDotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:Dotum;font-weight:\nbold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><span dir="ltr"></span>7. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; font-weight: bold;">Kembangkan kemampuan yang sudah ada<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-family: Cambria; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 130%;">Hal terakhir yaitu teruslah melatih dan mengembangkan kemampuan yang sudah dimiliki. Kemampuan yang awalnya biasa-biasa saja apabila diasah secara terus menerus pasti akan menghasilkan kemampuan yang luar biasa.</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><img class="img-responsive" src="../images/c4780529bfa8b051cbfe829dd81f6c4115.png" data-filename="Picture4.png" style="width: 25%;"><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-family: Cambria; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 130%;"><br></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-family: Cambria; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 130%;"><br></span></span></p><p class="MsoBodyText4" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Hobo Std'';">Kemudian, apabila kita sudah menemukan dan yakin tentang bakat yang kita miliki, apa lagi yang harus dilakukan?</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Hobo Std'';">?</span></p><p class="MsoBodyText4" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Hobo Std'';"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Papyrus;mso-default-font-family:Papyrus;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Papyrus;mso-latin-font-family:Papyrus;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Hal penting yang harus diperhatikan</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Pertama, mengembangkan bakat memerlukan waktu dan kemauan yang besar</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:\nCambria;mso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;\nmso-default-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:\nDotum;mso-greek-font-family:Dotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:Dotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:\nDotum;mso-latinext-font-family:Dotum;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"> Jangan cepat menyerah bila dirasa bakat yang dimiliki belum berkembang atau tidak menunjukkan peningkatan. Ada bakat yang memerlukan waktu dan latihan yang ekstra untuk mencapai potensi yang maksimal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Kedua, percaya pada diri sendiri</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-font-family:\nDotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:Dotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nDotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:Dotum;mso-hangul-font-family:\nDotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:Dotum;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">. Kamu yang menguasai bakat tersebut, kamu jugalah yang mengetahui kemampuan diri sendiri. Jangan takut bila melakukan kesalahan. Percayalah bahwa bakat pada dirimu suatu saat akan berguna bagi orang-orang disekitarmu.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Dotum;mso-latin-font-family:Dotum;mso-greek-font-family:\nDotum;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Dotum;mso-armenian-font-family:Dotum;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nDotum;mso-hangul-font-family:Dotum;mso-currency-font-family:Dotum;mso-latinext-font-family:\nDotum;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:130%;font-family:Cambria;mso-default-font-family:\nCambria;mso-ascii-f