t-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none">Usahakanlah untuk mengurangi suara-suara yang mengganggu.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"> Memang beberapa orang membutuhkan suara atau lagu dalam belajar, tetapi bagi beberapa orang ketenangan adalah kunci belajar. Temukanlah suasana yang kamu sukai! Kadang-kadang teman-teman atau keluarga juga bisa mengganggu lho. Nah, cobalah untuk sediakan waktu belajar tanpa gangguan mereka. Setelah belajar kamu bisa kok main lagi sama teman-teman atau berkumpul dengan keluarga. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:1.1612pt;\nmargin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper;\ntext-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Kalau masalah pencahayaan, biasanya</span><img class="img-responsive" src="../images/3343c348e6a962bfb52977aeed64b0940.png" data-filename="Picture6.png" style="width: 68.9104px; height: 81px; float: left;"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"> </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">lampu 75 Watt adalah yang terbaik</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">, tetapi juga jangan terlalu dekat dan letakkanlah berlawanan arah dengan tanganmu yang menulis, supaya cahayanya menyinari tulisanmu. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Suasana yang sejuk lebih baik daripada kepanasan.&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"></span><span lang="en-US"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Sediakanlah tempat yang luas untuk belajar</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">. Jangan sampai kamu</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic;"> sumpek </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">sendiri dengan kamar belajarmu. Akan lebih baik ketika kamu menyediakan waktu untuk berbenah dulu sebelum belajar.</span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Kursi yang memiliki sandaran tegak adalah kursi terbaik untuk belajar. Jangan sampai alas dudukmu </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">kelewat </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">nyaman, misalnya kasur nyaman yang sebenarnya untuk tidur bukan untuk belajar!</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Siapkanlah perlengkapan belajar,</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:\n10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"> misalnya buku, pensil, kertas, kopi, kamus, laptop, kalkulator, recorder atau yang lainnya, dekat denganmu dan dapat diraih dengan cepat. Jangan buang terlalu banyak waktu untuk </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">kelabakan </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">mencari barang-barang tersebut saat dibutuhkan.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"> </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-17.4193pt;line-height:150%;\ntab-stops:-1988in;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word;mso-level-number-format:\narabic;mso-level-text:&quot;%1\\.&quot;;mso-level-start-at:2;mso-level-indent:17.4193pt;\nmso-level-language:en-US"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">2.</span><span style="width:9.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-weight:\nbold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Siapkan mental untuk mengantisipasi ketegangan saat ujian.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:\n-1988in;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:\nArial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:\nArial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:\nArial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nArial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-curre