pan lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Buatlah tujuan yang adalah tujuan milikmu</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-weight:\nbold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"> Ini adalah hidupmu. Lakukan apa yang menjadi kerinduanmu. Tujuan yang kamu tetapkan sendiri jauh lebih baik daripada motivasi yang diberikan orang lain padamu. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Tuliskanlah tujuanmu. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Hal ini akan membantumu untuk tidak melupakan tujuanmu di tengah kesibukanmu. Tujuan yang ditulis dapat membantumu untuk meningkatkan komitmenmu. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Pastikanlah bahwa tujuanmu cukup menantang tetapi juga masuk akal.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"> Tujuan yang baik bukanlah hal yang terlalu mudah atau terlalu tidak mungkin untuk dicapai. Tujuan ini harus membuatmu berkembang. Tujuan yang menantang dan dapat dicapai akan membuatmu terus bersemangat.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Tujuanmu harus spesifik dan dapat diukur. </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:\nen-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Jangan berkata bahwa kamu inginkan pekerjaan yang lebih baik. Tanyakan dirimu: pekerjaan seperti apa? Pekerjaan dengan gaji berapa? Di bidang apa? Di mana? Membutuhkan keterampilan apa? Kapan? Buatlah tujuan secara spesifik dan kamu akan menghemat banyak waktu dan usaha jika telah menetapkan tujuan yang spesifik sebelumnya.</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Arial;mso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:\nArial;mso-latin-font-family:Arial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nArial;mso-armenian-font-family:Arial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:\nArial;mso-currency-font-family:Arial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;font-style:\nitalic;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:-1988in;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; ">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;tab-stops:\n-1988in;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Arial;\nmso-default-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-latin-font-family:\nArial;mso-greek-font-family:Arial;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Arial;mso-armenian-font-family:\nArial;mso-hebrew-font-family:Arial;mso-arabic-font-family:Arial;mso-currency-font-family:\nArial;mso-latinext-font-family:Arial;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US"><span style="line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'gimana-sih-cara-belajar-dan-menghindari-kecemasan-sebelum-ujian??', 'selfhelp', '2016-05-01 09:26:02', '2016-05-01 09:33:58');
