so-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;language:id;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;language:id;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:22.0644pt;text-indent:-10.4515pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Manajemen waktu yang buruk</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:22.0644pt;text-indent:-10.4515pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:22.0644pt;text-indent:-10.4515pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone"> </span><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;\nmso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;\nfont-weight:bold;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;\nmso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Prokrastinasi juga berarti tidak mengelola waktu secara bijak. Manajemen waktu yang buruk membuat kita tidak yakin dengan prioritas, tujuan, dan harapan-harapan yang kita buat. Biasanya tiba-tiba kita merasa “penuh” dengan tugas-tugas dan sebagai hasilnya, kita malah “menelantarkan” tugas-tugas kuliah.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;\nmso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;\nmso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -18pt;">Kesulitan berkonsentrasi</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -18pt;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;">Ketika duduk di meja belajar, terkadang kita</span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;">malah mengerjakan hal yang lain melamun, memandangi foto pacar, membaca majalah dsb. Lingkungan yang bising juga dapat memecah konsentrasi. Demikian juga kondisi kamar dan meja belajar yang kurang rapi.</span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;">Meja belajar yang tidak rapi akan membuat kamu semakin “penat” dan akhirnya memilih tempat tidur untuk belajar dan melakukan tugas. Keadaan yang tidak siap juga dapat memecah konsentrasimu. Misalnya jarak alat tulis dan buku yang jauh dari meja membuat kita harus bolak-balik mengambilnya dan akhirnya konsentrasimu malah terpecah.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -18pt;">Ketakutan dan kecemasan.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-weight: bold; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -18pt;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%; text-indent: 4.6451pt;">Ketika merasa penat dengan tugas dan takut gagal melewati ujian, biasanya reaksi emosi yang muncul adalah ketakutan dan kecemasan. Untuk mengatasi hal tersebut, seringkali kita malah fokus pada emosi yang kita rasakan dan bukan pada akar masalahnya. Sebagai hasilnya, kita justru menghabiskan banyak waktu dengan mengkhawatirkan ujian, tugas, dan praktikum berikutnya daripada menyelesaikan tugas-tugas tersebut.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:12.7741pt;text-indent:4.6451pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-3.4838pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Pikiran yang negatif</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-3.4838pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 1.5;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-3.4838pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 1.5;">Misalnya: “aku tidak dapat berhasil dalam segala hal”,</span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 1.5;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 1.5;">“aku tidak mendapat nilai A, aku&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -3.4838pt;">dan</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-3.4838pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -3.4838pt;">pikiran-pikiran negatif lainnya dapat menghentikanmu menyelesaikan tugas. Pikiran yang negatif</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:17.4193pt;text-indent:-3.4838pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\nline-height:119%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-word"><span style="font-family: Verdana; line-height: 119%; text-indent: -3.4838pt;">membuat motivasi kita melemah dan akhirnya kita semakin enggan mengerjakan tugas.</span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-left:12.7741pt;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:119%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:inter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;\nmso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-fami