nt-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none"><br></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;mso-level-number-format:bullet;mso-level-text:·;mso-level-size:10.0pt;\nmso-level-font-family:Symbol;mso-level-indent:0pt"><span style="direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·</span>&nbsp;<span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Ubahlah lingkunganmu: Pastikan cahaya yang cukup, suasana yang tenang, alat tulis dan buku-buku yang tepat dan tersedia didekatmu pada saat belajar. Jangan memilih posisi yang nyaman ketika belajar. Meja dan kursi tegak biasanya merupakan tempat paling baik (</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;font-weight:bold;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">tempat tidur bukan tempat belajar!</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Verdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;mso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latinext-font-family:Verdana;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none">). Jadilah orang yang rapi, misalnya dengan mengambil beberapa menit untuk merapikan mejamu. Dengan demikian kita dapat fokus dan berko</span><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">n</span><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:id;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">sentrasi seca</span><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">r</span><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;language:id;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">a maksimal dalam belajar maupun mengerjakan tugas.</span><span lang="id" style="font-family:&quot;Tw Cen MT&quot;;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="id" style="font-family: Verdana;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="id" style="font-family: Verdana;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="id" style="font-family: Verdana;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:\n150%"><span lang="id" style="font-family: Verdana;">Sumber: </span><a href="http://ub-counseling.buffalo.edu/stressprocrast.php"><span lang="id" style="font-family:Verdana;mso-default-font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-latin-font-family:Verdana;mso-greek-font-family:Verdana;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-armenian-font-family:Verdana;mso-hebrew-font-family:Verdana;\nmso-thai-font-family:Verdana;mso-currency-font-family:Verdana;mso-latinext-font-family:\nVerdana;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:navy;\nmso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100%;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:\nsingle;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;mso-liga