(9, 'Mengatasi Ketakutan Berbicara di Depan Umum ', 'Pernahkah kamu tiba-tiba merasa mual ketika akan presentasi?\nAtau muncul keringat dingin saat akan menjadi MC?\n', 'images/ed049a351573bd5beedb19cf1ad2063f.png', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:125%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Pernahkah kamu tiba-tiba merasa mual ketika akan presentasi?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:125%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Atau muncul keringat dingin saat akan menjadi MC?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:125%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Tatapan orang-orang di hadapanmu seolah-olah ingin mencecar atau menghakimimu?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:125%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">Bila kamu pernah mengalami hal-hal seperti di atas, berarti kamu mengalami ketakutan berbicara di depan umum (fear of public speaking).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:125%;text-align:\njustify;text-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="id" style="font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Nyala;mso-default-font-family:\nNyala;mso-ascii-font-family:Nyala;mso-latin-font-family:Nyala;mso-armenian-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nEuphemia;mso-latinext-font-family:Nyala;font-style:italic;language:id;\nmso-ansi-language:id;mso-ligatures:none">&nbsp;</span><span lang="id" style="font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Nyala;mso-default-font-family:\nNyala;mso-ascii-font-family:Nyala;mso-latin-font-family:Nyala;mso-armenian-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:\nEuphemia;mso-latinext-font-family:Nyala;language:id;mso-ansi-language:id;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;line-height:125%;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 125%; font-family: Corbel;">Sebenarnya apa itu </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 125%; font-family: Corbel; font-style: italic;">public speaking</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 125%; font-family: Corbel;">? Mengapa masih banyak orang&nbsp; takut berbicara di depan umum?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;line-height:125%;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-currency-font-family:Corbel;mso-latinext-font-family:\nCorbel;font-style:italic;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:\nnone">Public speaking </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:125%;font-family:Corbel;mso-default-font-family:Corbel;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-latin-font-family:Corbel;mso-greek-font-family:Corbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;mso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-currency-font-family:Corbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;language:en-US;\nmso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">adalah kemampuan berkomunikasi secara lisan tentang suatu topik di hadapan banyak orang. Tujuannya untuk&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:Nyala;\nmso-default-font-family:Nyala;mso-ascii-font-family:Nyala;mso-latin-font-family:\nNyala;mso-canadianabor-font-family:Euphemia;mso-currency-font-family:Euphemia;\nmso-latinext-font-family:Nyala;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;\nmso-ligatures:none"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="font-family: Corbel; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;">mempengaruhi, mengubah opini, mengajar, mendidik, memberikan penjelasan serta memberikan informasi kepada sekelompok orang tertentu.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Corbel; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;">Oleh karena itu, kemampuan berbicara di depan umum menjadi sangat penting dan diperlukan agar individu dapat menyampaikan pesan secara efektif kepada orang lain, terutama dalam hal persuasi dan motivasi.</span></p><p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;line-height:125%;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%"><span style="font-family: Corbel; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoBodyText3" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\nnewspaper;text-kashida-space:50%;line-height:125%;text-align:justify;\ntext-justify:newspaper;text-kashida-space:50%">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 129%; font-family: Corbel; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Glossophobia</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 129%; font-family: Corbel;"> – ketakutan berbicara di depan umum. Merupakan phobia yang paling umum terjadi pada manusia. Setidaknya 75% 