\nCorbel;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Carilah bahan-bahan yang sesuai dengan topik bahasan. Bila perlu cari sumber-sumber penelitian (ilmiah) yang berkaitan dengan topik. Apabila seseorang sudah menguasai topik yang akan disampaikan, maka kepercayaan diri akan muncul yang menjadi modal utama dalam </span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Corbel;\nmso-default-font-family:Corbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-greek-font-family:Corbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-currency-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:\nen-US;mso-ligatures:none">public speaking</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Corbel;\nmso-default-font-family:Corbel;mso-ascii-font-family:Corbel;mso-latin-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-greek-font-family:Corbel;mso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-hebrew-font-family:Corbel;mso-currency-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;font-style:italic;language:en-US;mso-ansi-language:\nen-US;mso-ligatures:none"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word;margin-bottom:0pt;line-height:150%;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-word"><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:Jokerman;mso-default-font-family:Jokerman;mso-ascii-font-family:\nJokerman;mso-latin-font-family:Jokerman;mso-greek-font-family:Corbel;\nmso-cyrillic-font-family:Corbel;mso-armenian-font-family:Corbel;mso-hebrew-font-family:\nCorbel;mso-currency-font-family:Corbel;mso-latinext-font-family:Corbel;\nlanguage:en-US;mso-ansi-language:en-US;mso-ligatures:none">Kedua</span><span lang="en-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-famil